=== scroll of identify ===
qty=1 identified buc=blessed -> a blessed scroll of identify
qty=1 identified buc=uncursed -> an uncursed scroll of identify
qty=1 identified buc=cursed -> a cursed scroll of identify
qty=1 identified buc=buc_unknown -> a scroll of identify
qty=1 unidentified -> a scroll labeled ZELGO MER
qty=1 called=id? -> a scroll called id?
qty=3 identified buc=blessed -> 3 blessed scroll of identifies
qty=3 identified buc=uncursed -> 3 uncursed scroll of identifies
qty=3 identified buc=cursed -> 3 cursed scroll of identifies
qty=3 identified buc=buc_unknown -> 3 scroll of identifies
qty=3 unidentified -> 3 scroll labeled ZELGO MERs
qty=3 called=id? -> 3 scroll called id?s
=== scroll of enchant weapon ===
qty=1 identified buc=blessed -> a blessed scroll of enchant weapon
qty=1 identified buc=uncursed -> an uncursed scroll of enchant weapon
qty=1 identified buc=cursed -> a cursed scroll of enchant weapon
qty=1 identified buc=buc_unknown -> a scroll of enchant weapon
qty=1 unidentified -> a scroll labeled DAIYEN FANSEN
qty=1 called=id? -> a scroll called id?
qty=3 identified buc=blessed -> 3 blessed scroll of enchant weapons
qty=3 identified buc=uncursed -> 3 uncursed scroll of enchant weapons
qty=3 identified buc=cursed -> 3 cursed scroll of enchant weapons
qty=3 identified buc=buc_unknown -> 3 scroll of enchant weapons
qty=3 unidentified -> 3 scroll labeled DAIYEN FANSENs
qty=3 called=id? -> 3 scroll called id?s
